    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"546447\">Benno Lossin</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/291565-Help/topic/scripts.2Fgenerate_rust_analyzer.2Epy.20fails.20on.20NixOS/near/565284250\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"413824\">Gary Guo</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/291565-Help/topic/scripts.2Fgenerate_rust_analyzer.2Epy.20fails.20on.20NixOS/near/565281297\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I got my rustc from oxalica's overlay rather than nixpkgs directly</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>I also do that</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Me3. Otherwise it is difficult to test with specific versions.</p>",
